name: Under the Papaya Tree
description:
This work is inspired by the lyric of the song "Kenakalan Remaja di Era Informatika" by my favorite local indie band "Efek Rumah Kaca", the lyric is "...Ketika birahi yang juara, etika menguap entah kemana..."

Eng. Translation : When lust wins, ethics evaporates somewhere~

Whether it's a outdoor fetish or whatever, they're always there and watching over you
